<p>
          Create professional, confident, and recruiter-friendly LinkedIn profile photos
          for women using AI. Copy clean prompts designed for careers, leadership,
          corporate roles, and personal branding.
        </p>
<!-- Author and Trust Signals -->
<div class="author-box" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 2rem auto;">
<div class="author-info">
<p><strong>Written by:</strong> PromptImageLab Team</p>
