<h2 class="mb-4 text-center">Top LinkedIn AI Prompts for Women</h2>
<div class="row g-4">
<!-- 1 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<h5>Professional</h5>
<small>Corporate · Clean</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p1">
                Create a professional LinkedIn profile photo for a woman wearing a well-tailored blazer in a rich jewel
                tone over a clean white silk blouse, photographed from the chest up against a smooth neutral grey studio
                background. The studio lighting is carefully positioned with a large softbox at 45 degrees to create
                gentle, flattering shadows that sculpt the cheekbones and jawline. The expression is both confident and
                approachable — a natural slight smile with direct eye contact that communicates warmth, competence, and
                professional authority. The image is sharp and high-resolution with natural skin tones and hair
                perfectly styled, optimized for LinkedIn's circular profile crop. The result looks like a photograph
                taken by a premium corporate photographer.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p1')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 2 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<h5>Formal Executive</h5>
<small>Leadership · Premium</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p2">
                Convert my photo into a polished LinkedIn profile picture of a woman in formal executive business attire
                — a structured black blazer with padded shoulders over a crisp white blouse, projecting authority and
                leadership. The studio lighting setup features a large softbox key light creating soft, even
                illumination with a fill reflector on the opposite side to prevent harsh shadows. The focus is
                razor-sharp on the eyes and facial features with a gentle depth-of-field blur on the shoulders, creating
                a premium editorial look. The expression is composed and authoritative — a poised, direct gaze that
                communicates executive-level professionalism and decisive leadership. The background is a seamless rich
                charcoal grey that complements the formal attire.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p2')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 3 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<h5>Corporate Style</h5>
<small>Trust · Authority</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p3">
                Create a corporate-style LinkedIn profile photo for a woman dressed in refined business attire — a
                tailored pencil skirt suit or structured blazer in navy blue or charcoal, accessorized with understated
                pearl earrings. The background is minimal and clean with a soft gradient from light grey to white,
                eliminating all distractions. Balanced three-point lighting creates even, professional illumination
                across the face with gentle modeling shadows that add dimension without being dramatic. The expression
                conveys trust, competence, and quiet authority — essential qualities for corporate professionals, legal
                practitioners, and financial industry leaders. The composition is perfectly centered and optimized for
                professional networking platforms.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p3')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 4 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<h5>Modern Professional</h5>
<small>Startup · Tech</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p4">
                Create a modern LinkedIn profile picture for a woman wearing contemporary business attire — a clean,
                fitted blazer over a premium turtleneck or sleek crew-neck top in a neutral tone, reflecting the style
                of tech leaders and creative professionals. The background is clean and simple with a soft, warm
                ambiance. Soft natural lighting from a large window creates an authentic, modern feel with gentle
                shadows and warm, healthy skin tones. The expression is friendly and confident with a natural, unstaged
                quality that conveys innovation and contemporary professionalism, perfect for women in technology,
                design, and creative leadership roles on LinkedIn.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p4')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 5 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<h5>Casual Professional</h5>
<small>Smart Casual</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p5">
                Transform my photo into a smart casual LinkedIn profile picture for a woman wearing a fitted blazer over
                a clean top, or a stylish silk blouse in a flattering color. The expression is warm and genuine — a
                relaxed, friendly smile that makes the viewer feel at ease while maintaining an air of professionalism
                and poise. Natural lighting from a diffused source creates a bright, airy atmosphere with soft, organic
                shadows. The background is simple and uncluttered. The overall image projects a modern, personable
                professional who is approachable and collaborative — ideal for HR professionals, marketing leaders, and
                customer-facing roles.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p5')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 6 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<h5>Headshot</h5>
<small>Recruiter Friendly</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p6">
                Create a clean, close-up LinkedIn headshot for a woman framed tightly from the collar to just above the
                head, ensuring the face dominates at least 70% of the image. Every facial detail is captured with
                extraordinary sharpness — bright, clear eyes with visible catchlights, well-defined brows, and natural,
                healthy skin with subtle makeup that enhances without overpowering. The background is softly blurred
                with a smooth bokeh that provides gentle separation without distraction. Professional studio lighting
                from a beauty dish creates flattering, even illumination with a subtle nose shadow adding dimension.
                This recruiter-friendly headshot is specifically optimized for LinkedIn's profile picture display,
                making a strong first impression in search results and connection requests.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p6')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 7 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<h5>Personal Branding</h5>
<small>Confidence · Identity</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p7">
                Create a LinkedIn profile photo for personal branding — a woman dressed in a modern business outfit that
                reflects her unique professional identity, such as a structured blazer in a bold yet tasteful color over
                a minimalist top. Natural studio lighting with soft diffusion creates a warm, authentic feel with gentle
                rim lighting along the shoulders for a polished edge. The background is clean with subtle, warm tones
                that complement the outfit. The expression communicates genuine confidence and authenticity — the look
                of someone who knows her worth and her craft. The composition uses a slight three-quarter angle for
                dynamic visual impact, creating a personal brand image that is both memorable and professional.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p7')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 8 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<h5>Leadership</h5>
<small>Authority · Impact</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p8">
                Create a leadership-style LinkedIn profile picture for a woman in premium formal attire — a meticulously
                tailored dark blazer with a silk blouse, accessorized with elegant but understated jewelry. The subject
                is photographed against a neutral background that recedes into soft shadow at the edges, creating a
                powerful, authoritative frame. High-quality studio lighting features a large key light creating defined,
                editorial-quality shadows that sculpt the face with precision, while a subtle rim light adds elegant
                separation along the shoulders. The body language communicates strong leadership presence — squared
                shoulders, elevated chin, and a direct, commanding gaze. This is a premium executive portrait suitable
                for senior women leaders, board members, and C-suite professionals.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p8')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 9 -->
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
<div class="card">
<h5>Minimal</h5>
<small>Clean · Simple</small>
<div class="prompt-box" id="p9">
                Create a minimal LinkedIn profile photo for a woman with a clean, contemporary aesthetic. The subject
                wears a simple, well-fitted solid-colored top or sweater in a flattering neutral tone, photographed
                against a clean, plain background in white, light grey, or subtle warm beige. Soft, diffused lighting
                from a single large source creates gentle, natural shadowing with a modern, editorial quality. The face
                is clearly focused and prominently framed, occupying the majority of the composition. The image has
                minimal post-processing with natural colors and authentic skin tones, embodying a clean, professional
                style that lets the person's genuine warmth and character speak for itself.
              </div>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText('p9')">COPY PROMPT</button>
</div>
</div>
